uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model

Class DIdentity

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.CIdentity
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.DIdentity

  • public class DIdentity
extends CIdentity
    Represents the identity for a frames-based entity derived from a particular class or field in the Object Model (OM).

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      DIdentity(java.lang.Class<?> dClass)
      Constructs identity for the specified OM class, with the fully-qualified class-name as the identifier and the label being heuristically-generated from the simple class-name (via the KLabel-mechanism).
      DIdentity(java.lang.String fieldName)
      Constructs identity for the specified OM field, with the field-name itself as the identifier and the label being heuristically-generated from the field-name (via the KLabel-mechanism).
